tasks.name: Canadian DOT issues with Air
tasks.notes:
Issue 1: Any flight that originates from Canada should be priced in Canadian Dollars. Note: we can show in CAD but charging in CAD would be a big effort.

Issue 2: They want fees displayed a certain way.

Issue 3: They want the charges renamed

Issue 4: They want 9/11 fee put into the base price instead of broken out as a fee. 

Note: I believe for issues 2-4 they are going to say that the DOT should ask the GDS to change it in their data feed.
